title: 170:  Bucky's Top 5 QBs, Miami TE David Njoku and more
itunes:title: 170:  Bucky's Top 5 QBs, Miami TE David Njoku and more
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks reveal their perfect pairings for the first two picks of every team in the AFC South and AFC West. Bucky Brooks also reveals his Top 5 QBs in the 2017 NFL Draft class. Miami TE David Njoku joins the show and Bucky also talks to Dolphins general manager Chris Grier about the state of the franchise. The scouting stories continue to roll in as Chargers general manager Tom Telesco tells about one of his most surprising moments on the road.
